{"tid":1265790,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［防分化］連登仔從今日開始要做的三件事","createTime":"2019-06-29T11:03:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T02:47:21.000Z","uid":265443,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"808f9f7caa19dd79abb9a4dd98bdd4829b28feb5","tid":1265790,"uid":265443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T11:03:52.000Z","msg":"<ins>1。習慣懷疑&amp;提防</ins><br />\n所有人都需要提防，小心一切標題有<span style=\"color: red;\">「突發」</span>兩個字嘅消息（或者類似即時消息）<br />\n<br />\n<ins>2。有懷疑三五毛嘅id, <span style=\"color: red;\">勿封鎖</span>，<span style=\"color: green;\">反追蹤</span></ins><br />\n可以係關鍵時刻警醒人提防，知己知彼，百戰百勝<br />\n<br />\n<ins>3。讀完呢篇文章，從意識上裝備自己</ins><br />\n我地要對抗嘅係邪惡冷血嘅中共，就算疑神疑鬼d都無計<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/21671/反送中-年輕人-21671/提防中共的各式反撲技倆\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F21671%2F%E5%8F%8D%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD-%E5%B9%B4%E8%BC%95%E4%BA%BA-21671%2F%E6%8F%90%E9%98%B2%E4%B8%AD%E5%85%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%90%84%E5%BC%8F%E5%8F%8D%E6%92%B2%E6%8A%80%E5%80%86&d=FYZ0PdCaIZeH%2BWUkJYSmqyEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=fe5fdd66\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcnews.com/article/21671/反送中-年輕人-21671/提防中共的各式反撲技倆</a><br />\n<br />\n呢一刻或者第一個需要提防嘅就係樓主我，你咁諗我會好欣慰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n對手好叻玩分化，唔止物理裝備，<strong><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">我地意識都要裝備起黎</span></strong></strong>，我唔想因爲內部分化而輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以下開放討論"},{"pid":"a55440f170c9a5f7e92eaa847d2727aec471b97a","tid":1265790,"uid":265443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T11:06:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"564a541628962f3857d41fe38556fc9408cc4865","tid":1265790,"uid":265443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T11:07:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5f1382c56756f7b3a912af94cfc34983da650dc9","tid":1265790,"uid":265443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T12:48:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ebacb699ede08fed6cc9e79e29242e35563cf41b","tid":1265790,"uid":265443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T02:38:59.000Z","msg":"手土"},{"pid":"ebc890ea80af16fcd88c16e61b00d467002acd1c","tid":1265790,"uid":17232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T02:47:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人到而家仲未識真正咁運用三角鐵馬<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1267307\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1267307</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fEkrd2R.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfEkrd2R.gif&h=d8974866&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fEkrd2R.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfEkrd2R.gif&h=d8974866&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fEkrd2R.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfEkrd2R.gif&h=d8974866&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Keuoggc.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKeuoggc.gif&h=0ba950e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Keuoggc.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKeuoggc.gif&h=0ba950e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Keuoggc.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKeuoggc.gif&h=0ba950e7&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}